            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Herculi <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Sentius Bantiu<supplied reason="lost">s</supplied> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> Baeb<supplied reason="lost">ius R</supplied>usticus <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> Octaviu<supplied reason="lost">s Ono</supplied>mastus VIvi<supplied reason="lost">ri</supplied> <lb n="5"/>ex summis hon<supplied reason="lost">ora</supplied>riis quas colle<supplied reason="lost">gio</supplied> <lb n="6"/>nautarum debuerant <expan><abbr>adi</abbr><ex>ectis</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>HS |(duobus milibus) CC posuerunt
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Erhalten ist der Mittelteil einer Statuenbasis; mehrere Dübellöcher auf der Oberseite. Fundort: nach G. Alföldy vielleicht aus Arilica (Peschiera) verschleppt. Lesung nach G. Alföldy.</p>
            </div>
